article.headline: Wright double-double powers SIU Edwardsville over Lindenwood 91-63
article.description: — Lamar Wright had 20 points and 10 rebounds to power SIU Edwardsville to a 91-63 victory over Lindenwood on Thursday night.
article.linkText: Wright double-double powers SIU Edwardsville over Lindenwood 91-63
article.story: EDWARDSVILLE, Ill. -- — Lamar Wright had 20 points and 10 rebounds to power SIU Edwardsville to a 91-63 victory over Lindenwood on Thursday night. Damarco Minor totaled 16 points, seven rebounds and seven assists for the Cougars (14-12, 7-6 Ohio Valley Conference). Shamar Wright hit three 3-pointers and scored 15. The Lions (8-18, 2-11) were led by Jeremiah Talton's 18 points. Keenon Cole added 14 points and 10 rebounds. Isaac Ondekane had nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
